high_descs: Turn toward the sink and grab the soap on the top right corner of the sink.
Turn to the left with the soapbar in hand.
Turn back towards the sink and back up.
Place the soapbar in the sink and fill it with water, then drain the sink.
Pick up soap and walk towards the toilet with soap in hand.
Place the soapbar on top of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: The robot will take the SoapBar from the sink, wet it, and then place on top of Toilet.

high_descs: In the toilet room turn around and take right to the sink.
Head toward the sink and reach for the soapbar on the sink.
Pick up the soap from the sink.
Put the soapbar in the sink and clean it.
Pick on the cleaned soap on the toilet.
Head toward the soapbar on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Pick the SoapBar, clean it and keep it around the Toilet.
